{"tid":1537094,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"文宣真係要進步一下","createTime":"2019-09-03T20:37:15.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-04T01:17:58.000Z","uid":175599,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"ef9701295668eb20a723630c7773dbd216d93365","tid":1537094,"uid":175599,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T20:37:15.000Z","msg":"見到隔離post南亞手足咁勇武，<br />\n其實文宣真係要翻譯下巴基斯坦文、印度文、尼泊爾文<br />\n起碼比佢地清楚咩局勢<br />\n佢地又勇<br />\n有利助攻<br />\n佢地平時都比黑警欺壓得多<br />\n係時候激起埋佢地既雄心對抗港共<br />\n同佢地講中國唔會收容南亞人士<br />\n香港歸共佢地遲早要返鄉下<br />\n佢地好多都唔似隔離post ust仔同利君雅咁清楚香港事<br />\n最重要中文佢地真係唔太好<br />\n所以真係有需要佢地語言既文宣<br />\n大家身邊朋友有冇邊個係南亞巴<br />\n可以幫下手寫文宣/翻譯"},{"pid":"8e6059a9e145baaa1c18a03e3dadd7ca10bb0066","tid":1537094,"uid":267425,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T20:37:30.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>解散警隊 刻不容緩</strong></span></span><br />\n我屌曬你地老母快啲推第六大訴求<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1536852\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1536852</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/MKrrRfp.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FMKrrRfp.jpg&h=a94ed6e8&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"8db0b59aca181f24a0f011e028ccb65b883a95c9","tid":1537094,"uid":268725,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T20:37:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/8B39Niu.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F8B39Niu.png&h=c9eeccd1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"63fc95b99adecb7964a143c5fb7d2f3d2248d353","tid":1537094,"uid":41245,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T20:53:24.000Z","msg":"頂，已經有英文啦<br />\n大佬，做香港人唔識中文都算<br />\n有英文啦<br />\n仲要譯埋佢地語言<br />\n會唔會太妹仔大過主人婆呀？<br />\n講明we connect少數族裔，我支持<br />\n但譯做佢地語言就不了"},{"pid":"3bb61fc37258bfba0b99fe56ffa496b017d7c42d","tid":1537094,"uid":52727,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T01:17:58.000Z","msg":"【教學】將Facebook/Youtube 影片文宣轉換成Twitter 文宣<br />\r\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1537277\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1537277</a><br />\r\n<br />\r\n1. 註冊Twitter 帳號。<br />\r\n2. 找到要post 上Twitter 的影片。<br />\r\n3. 複制facebook影片連結貼上到以下網頁 (需要登入及縛定Twitter 帳戶， facebook影片分享必需是公開)。<br />\r\n<br />\r\n<a href=\"https://transferring-videos.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftransferring-videos.com&d=8FXSm2SwW1drj%2BZzPONh3F3VpWtqcNNCzs9YdIyDBYU%3D&h=d0e1ccff\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://transferring-videos.com</a><br />\r\n<br />\r\n4. 等待轉換時輸入英文標題，及加上 #chinazi 等 hash tag。<br />\r\n5. 選擇發佈至 Twitter。<br />\r\n<br />\r\n6. 【重要】我諗大家嘅Twitter應該都冇乜人follow, 記得copy自己Twitter post 嘅link, 然後貼上到名人的Twitter post 上！<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\r\n<br />\r\n我做咗幾日已經多咗好多外國人睇，甚至開始有支那打手過黎留言。<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}